title: Introducing the BVP Award - Week 8, Reviewed
description:
Holly, Jason, and Spencer come to you bearing the following tidings (I'm not totally sure what tidings are but I am also too lazy to look):
- Behold our SOONER SCHOONER CHAOS POWERS
- Some early nominees for the 2019 BVP, given to college football's most college football player
- ILLINOIS LET'S GOOOOOOOOOOOOO
- Butts
- Now you know a single thing about Ball State!
- Tell a friend to attend our live show in Jacksonville
